[div class=p 
	[a class=intlink href=/Users/Profile/eien86 
		"eien86
	]a
	": A simplistic auto-scrolling space shoot em up homebrew game consisting of a single level with 5 stages. The scrolling speed seems constant throughout the gameplay so it's unlikely we'll see any faster movies. In spite of that, the author makes sure to eliminate all destructible enemies and objectives.
	$LF
]div
